sect1.programlisting:
class Bootstrap extends Zend_Application_Bootstrap_Bootstrap
{
    // ...

    protected function _initSidebar()
    {
        $this->bootstrap('View');
        $view = $this->getResource('View');

        $view->placeholder('sidebar')
             // "prefix" -> markup to emit once before all items in collection
             ->setPrefix("<div class=\"sidebar\">\n    <div class=\"block\">\n")
             // "separator" -> markup to emit between items in a collection
             ->setSeparator("</div>\n    <div class=\"block\">\n")
             // "postfix" -> markup to emit once after all items in a collection
             ->setPostfix("</div>\n</div>");
    }

    // ...
}

class UserController extends Zend_Controller_Action
{
    // ...

    public function preDispatch()
    {
        // ...

        $this->view->render('user/_sidebar.phtml');

        // ...
    }

    // ...
}

sect1.para:
There are a large number of things you can do by combining placeholders and layout scripts;
experiment with them, and read the relevant manual sections for more
information.
